    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Travassosinema viatorum n. sp. Female.A. Oesophageal region, lateral view. B. Tail, lateral view. C. Cephalic end, lateral view (reconstructed from SEM images). D. Vagina, lateral view. E. Genital tract, lateral view. F. Habitus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181893/files/figure.png" ;
