<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181895>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Travassosinema viatorum n. sp., SEM images. Female. A. Cephalic end, en face view. B. Cephalic end, lateral view. C. Vulva, ventral view. D. Anus and phasmid, lateral view. E. Tail, lateral view. Scale bars: A, B, C, D. 10 µm. E. 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181895/files/figure.png" ;
